    <item>
      <title>Youth Accreditation Mobility – Erasmus&#43; KA150-YOU</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/erasmus/2026/youth-accreditation-mobility/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/erasmus/2026/youth-accreditation-mobility/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;youth-accreditation-mobility--erasmus-ka150-you-&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Youth Accreditation Mobility – Erasmus+ KA150-YOU 🇹🇷&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#youth-accreditation-mobility--erasmus-ka150-you-&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Youth Exchange (YE)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;📍 Sakarya, Türkiye&lt;br&gt;&#xA;📅 28 March – 5 April 2026&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;about&#34;&gt;&#xA;  About&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#about&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This Erasmus+ youth mobility brought together participants from seven European countries to foster active citizenship, leadership, and intercultural understanding through non-formal education and collaborative learning.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The project provided an opportunity to exchange perspectives with young people from different backgrounds while exploring topics such as digital competences, entrepreneurship, sustainability, and European values.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Green Horizons: Youth for Sustainable Communities</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/erasmus/2025/green-horizons/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/erasmus/2025/green-horizons/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;green-horizons-youth-for-sustainable-communities-&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Green Horizons: Youth for Sustainable Communities 🇪🇸&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#green-horizons-youth-for-sustainable-communities-&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Youth Exchange (YE)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;📍 La Zarza de Pumareda, Salamanca, Spain&lt;br&gt;&#xA;📅 13–19 July 2025&lt;br&gt;&#xA;🏢 Organized by &lt;strong&gt;Fundación Plan B Educación Social&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;about&#34;&gt;&#xA;  About&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#about&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Green Horizons: Youth for Sustainable Communities&lt;/em&gt; was an Erasmus+ Youth Exchange that brought together young people from different European countries to explore sustainability, climate action, and active participation through non-formal education and intercultural learning.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
